{"tid":1429314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥到訪天水圍警署感謝警隊努力維護法紀","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:04:49.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"84cf003575048b28349f90f235154d601539e579","tid":1429314,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190807_20190807-210038.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190807_20190807-210038.jpg&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=5aef2861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190807_20190807-210038.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥，在未有安排傳媒採訪下，到訪天水圍警署，了解近日警署設施受示威者破壞的情況，並探望駐守的警務人員，她感謝警隊在非常困難的情況下努力維護法紀。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又在食物及衛生局長陳肇始陪同下，視察天水圍新公眾街市的選址，及到大圍了解街市改善工程進展，她說，會在十月公布的施政報告中，提出更多改善民生的措施。林鄭月娥在行程中與多名區內居民交談，居民對社會議題表達不同意見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1150173&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1150173%26csid%3D261_341&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=7ccea52e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1150173&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"739d87a27dfd939128c2f1c49aa7cc6713e06ca2","tid":1429314,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190807_20190807-210038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190807_20190807-210038.jpg&h=2aa511fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06496ddf0b32907a9dada73fbcdde01bcfe8b9fe","tid":1429314,"uid":45007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0